[09/12/2019 02:01:52] <font color="#0000ff">(Gritos)</font>
[09/12/2019 02:02:12] <font color="#ffff00">¡Empujen, carajo!</font>
[09/12/2019 02:02:32] <font color="#ffff00">¡Al ataque!</font>
