[09/12/2019 05:00:40] <font color="#ffffff">Salud.</font>
[09/12/2019 05:00:42] <font color="#ffff00">Y gracias.</font>
[09/12/2019 05:00:49] <font color="#ffffff">(Mugido)</font>
[09/12/2019 05:00:52] <font color="#ffff00">"Hora de ponerse en marcha</font>
